    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK593">
<l>ākka miḻantēmeṉ ṟallāvā rūkka </l>
<l> moruvantaṅ kaittuṭai yār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They who are possessed of enduring energy will not trouble themselves, saying, "we have lost our property."</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
